{"type": "article", "id": 21348, "title": "旋转台灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-01-27T07:30:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 13, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122306vHkMKLQnDcJ6Tr12.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这盏木质台灯像一个小的摄像机，但设计者却是从宠物身上获得灵感。它的三角形支架像动物的腿，而方形的灯罩是动物的头，黑色的圆形按钮像是动物的五官，有可爱的神情，也是取意一种陪伴。灯头可以顺着轴 360 度旋转，用来调整光的方向。这盏灯目前还没有出售，有兴趣可以<a href=\"http://macoshdesign.pl/pet/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里查看这家波兰的工作室主页。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261509113nWM1l40SoB8JN9O.gif\" width=\"1050\" height=\"812\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.77333333\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150912b1aYItLcZwWzU0Hf.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"698\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6647619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150913viS4bKDCaf5rkdFu.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"698\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6647619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150913wsUQpViatCXfE4Ry.jpg\" width=\"1050\" height=\"738\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.70285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}